      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that remains in original, factory-fresh condition.",
